
* required libraries

3rd party:

- dbus
- boost 1.53 (for assertion)

sudo apt-get install dbus libdbus-1-dev 

own:

- utils (logger)
- threcon (optionally)

* start on Ubuntu Server 14.04

- start Xvfb

$ Xvfb -screen 0 800x600x16 -ac &

- start Skype

$ DISPLAY=:0 skype &

- start example

$ DISPLAY=:0 ./example
